pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 50, 4, 30]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: header-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 48, 300, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>ROI  //  العائد على الاستثمار</p>
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 90, 700, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      text: |
        <p>نتائج قابلة للقياس</p>
      wrap: false
  - elementId: r1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 170, 370, 250]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"
  - elementId: r1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 195, 320, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>+35%</p>
  - elementId: r1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 265, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>زيادة في مبيعات الوحدات</p>
  - elementId: r1-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [85, 305, 320, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF99"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>بفضل CRM الذكي ومتابعة العملاء آلياً</p>
  - elementId: r2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [455, 170, 370, 250]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$dark"
  - elementId: r2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 195, 320, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>-60%</p>
  - elementId: r2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 265, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>تقليل وقت المتابعة</p>
  - elementId: r2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 305, 320, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#FFFFFF99"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>أتمتة المتابعة والتذكير والتواصل مع العملاء</p>
  - elementId: r3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [850, 170, 370, 250]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: r3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 195, 320, 60]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$dark"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>100%</p>
  - elementId: r3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 265, 320, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 20
      color: "$dark"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>متوافق مع PDPL</p>
  - elementId: r3-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [875, 305, 320, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "#1A1A1AAA"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      text: |
        <p>حماية كاملة لبيانات العملاء والامتثال</p>
  - elementId: bottom-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 450, 1160, 80]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$muted"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>بناءً على تجارب حقيقية لشركات عقارية سعودية استخدمت Dealix. النتائج تختلف حسب حجم الشركة وتطبيقها للمنصة.</p>
